- Install a Nerd font (preferably UbuntoMono Nerd font)
- Modify the JSON file
	- map paste to ctrl-shift-v
	- map copy to ctrl-shift-c
	- in the JSON settings add `"multiLinePasteWarning": false` in the global section

Reccommendations
	- Use "Windows Terminal" instead of the ubuntu terminal to use the wsl linux
